104    public static Map<Integer, Class<? extends HistoryLog>> LOG_MESSAGE_IDS = new HashMap<>();
105    public static Map<Class<? extends HistoryLog>, Integer> LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID = new HashMap<>();
106
107    static {
108        for (Class<? extends HistoryLog> clazz : LOG_MESSAGE_TYPES) {
109            try {
110                LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.put(clazz.newInstance().typeId(), clazz);
111                LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID.put(clazz, clazz.newInstance().typeId());
112            } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
113                L.e(TAG, String.format("could not instantiate %s", clazz), e);
114                e.printStackTrace();
115            }
116        }
117    }
118
119    public static HistoryLog parse(byte[] rawStream) {
120        // Little endian, unsigned
121        int typeId = rawStream[0];
122        if (typeId < 0) {
123            typeId += 512;
124        }
125        if (rawStream[1] > 0) {
126            typeId += 256 * rawStream[1];
127        }
128//        if (typeId % 256 != typeId) {
129//            L.w(TAG, "typeId "+typeId+" is being corrected to "+(typeId % 256));
130//            typeId = typeId % 256;
131//        }
132        HistoryLog ret = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, typeId);
133        if (ret instanceof UnknownHistoryLog) {
134            L.w(TAG, "retry1 HistoryLog parse on typeId " + typeId + " => " + ((byte) typeId));
135            HistoryLog two = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, (byte) typeId);
136            if (!(two instanceof UnknownHistoryLog)) {
137                return two;
138            }
139            if ((byte) typeId < 0) {
140                L.w(TAG, "retry2 HistoryLog parse on typeId " + ((byte) typeId) + " => " + (((byte) typeId) + 512));
141                HistoryLog three = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, (((byte) typeId) + 512));
142                if (!(three instanceof UnknownHistoryLog)) {
143                    return three;
144                }
145            }
146        }
147        return ret;
148    }
149
150    private static HistoryLog parseWithTypeId(byte[] rawStream, int typeId) {
151        HistoryLog historyLog = null;
152        if (!LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.containsKey(typeId)) {
153            L.t(TAG, "unknown HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
154            historyLog = new UnknownHistoryLog();
155            historyLog.parse(rawStream);
156            L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, UNKNOWN): %s", typeId, Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream)));
157            return historyLog;
158        }
159
160        try {
161            historyLog = LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.get(typeId).newInstance();
162        } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
163            L.e(TAG, "could not instantiate "+typeId, e);
164            e.printStackTrace();
165            return null;
166        }
167
168        String name = MessageHelpers.lastTwoParts(historyLog.getClass().getName());
169        L.t(TAG, "found matching "+name+" HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
170        historyLog.parse(rawStream);
171        L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, %s): %s", typeId, name, historyLog.toString()));
172        return historyLog;
173    }
